---
title: Mumbai Crumbed Fish with Spiced Roast Veggie Toss & Yoghurt
description: A crumbed fish schnitzel is a classic that we’ll never get tired of - but who’s in for a flavour twist? We are! Let’s throw warm Mumbai spices right into the crumb, and serve it alongside spiced roast veggies and cooling yoghurt. Yum!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/664ed9920ab4934df86335be-250d1ab6.jpeg
